Sicario;;85;;92;;R;;After rising through the ranks of her male-dominated profession, idealistic FBI agent Kate Macer (Emily Blunt) receives a top assignment. Recruited by mysterious government official Matt Graver (Josh Brolin), Kate joins a task force for the escalating war against drugs. Led by the intense and shadowy Alejandro (Benicio Del Toro), the team travels back-and-forth across the U.S.-Mexican border, using one cartel boss (Bernardo Saracino) to flush out a bigger one (Julio Cesar Cedillo).;;Mystery & thriller,Crime,Drama;;Denis Villeneuve;;2015;;Emily Blunt,Benicio Del Toro,Josh Brolin,Victor Garber,Jon Bernthal,Daniel Kaluuya,Jeffrey Donovan,Raoul Max Trujillo,Julio Cedillo,Bernardo Gallegos;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sicario_2015